Module chav1961.purelib

Package chav1961.purelib.fsys.interfaces

This package contains description of general File system interfaces.

Since:
0.0.1
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataWrapperInterface
    This interface describes a data wrapper to get information about the file system entity.
    FileSystemInterface
    This interface describes an abstract file system.
    FileSystemInterface.FileSystemListCallbackInterface
    This interface uses as callback for processing directories content (see list(IFileSystemListCallback) and list(String,IFileSystemListCallback)).
    FileSystemInterfaceDescriptor
    This interface describes file system drivers in user-friendly form.
    RMIDataWrapperInterface
    Don't use this interface for any purposes!
